selecttoggle
............

@{b}SYNTAX@{ub}
     SelectToggle

@{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
     This function selects or deselects the current record, depending
     on its selection state.

@{b}PARAMETERS@{ub}
@{b}RETURN@{ub}
     always RC = 0.

@{b}SEE ALSO@{ub}
@{"selectall" Link "selectall"}, @{"selecttoggle" Link "selecttoggle"}
     , @{"selectstring" Link "selectstring"}, @{"selectgroup" Link "selectgroup"}
